    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine starts up without hesitation and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. The interior is clean and has been smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. On the exterior, the paint still holds a great shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with regular use. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, making this a dependable and comfortable choice for its next owner.",
