    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways! It runs smoothly and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels for yourself. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 29500.0,
