      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the platform's known lateral stress points. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul.",
